'''华为应用市场'''（{{lang-en|Huawei AppGallery}}）是[[华为|华为]]为[[Android|Android]]系统，[[鸿蒙_(操作系统)|鸿蒙操作系统]]及[[Windows_11|Windows 11]]开发的[[应用程序|应用程序]]管理平台，是[[华为移动服务|华为移动服务]]（HMS）的一环，在超过170个国家的华为设备上搭载<ref>{{cite web |title=HUAWEI AppGallery and HUAWEI Mobile Services (HMS) {{!}} TELUS Support |url=https://www.telus.com/en/bc/support/article/huawei-appgallery-and-mobile-services-hms |website=www.telus.com |accessdate=2020-10-31 |archive-date=2020-09-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200919231611/https://www.telus.com/en/bc/support/article/huawei-appgallery-and-mobile-services-hms |dead-url=no }}</ref>，目前是世界第三大应用市场<ref>{{cite web |last1=Huawei |first1=Studio 61 for |title=Paid Content: Best apps in the Huawei AppGallery |url=https://www.cnet.com/paid-content/news/best-apps-in-the-huawei-appgallery/ |website=CNET |accessdate=2020-10-31 |language=en |archive-date=2020-10-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201031144826/https://www.cnet.com/paid-content/news/best-apps-in-the-huawei-appgallery/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 发布背景 ==
在未被[[美國對中華人民共和國的制裁|美国制裁]]前，华为应用市场同[[中国大陆|中国大陆]]其他手机厂商的“应用商店”一样，是华为官方基于安卓开发的[[EMUI|EMUI]]的应用市场。2019年5月，[[Google|Google]]停止了对华为手机的[[Google_Play服務|Google Play服務]]（GMS）支持<ref>{{cite web |title=The Huawei ban explained: A complete timeline and everything you need to know |url=https://www.androidauthority.com/huawei-google-android-ban-988382/ |website=Android Authority |accessdate=2020-10-31 |date=2020-08-25 |archive-date=2019-06-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190609191845/https://www.androidauthority.com/huawei-google-android-ban-988382/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。为此，华为启用了自研的华为移动服务（HMS）代替，华为应用市场由此代替[[Google_Play|Google Play]]成为搭载HMS服务的华为手机的官方应用市场<ref>{{cite web |title=AppGallery is Huawei's alternative to Google's Play Store on Android |url=https://www.xda-developers.com/appgallery-huawei-alternative-google-play-store-android/ |website=xda-developers |accessdate=2020-10-31 |date=2019-09-22 |archive-date=2020-10-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201029012054/https://www.xda-developers.com/appgallery-huawei-alternative-google-play-store-android/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 现状 ==
